title: LARGE 2-STORY TWINHOME IN A GREAT LOCATION
posting_body: ['PLEASE NOTE.', 'THE PROPERTY IS AVAILABLE NOW.', 'THE TENANTS LEASE IS ENDING ON AUGUST 31, 2022, BUT DUE TO THE FAMILY ISSUES THEY MOVED OUT EARLIER.', 'Twin Home is located in Coon Rapids at the end of Cul-de-Sac Road.', 'It has Very Private 0.2 Acre Fully Fenced Wooded Yard.', 'Property Features:', 'Three Bedrooms - Two Bedrooms on Upper Lvl, One Bedroom on Main Lvl.', 'Two Baths - 3/4 Bath on Main Lvl, Full Bath on Upper Lvl.', 'Large Kitchen with window, Plenty of Cabinets for Storage.', 'Walkout Main Level to the Deck', 'Hardwood Flooring Throughout the Property.', 'Build-In Microwave, Washer, Dryer, Dishwasher, Stove, Refrigerator', 'Oversized Attached Two Car Garage with Door Opener.', 'Central Air Conditioner.', 'Couple Month Old Water Heater.', 'Good Size Dog Kennel on the Fenced Backyard.', 'Rent $1799, Plus Tenants Pay All Utilities, Security Deposit - $1799', 'First Month Rent, Last Month Rent and Damage Deposit are due at the time of signing the Lease Agreement.', 'Some Pets are accepted with additional rent/fee.', 'Dogs Must be 20 Pounds or Less when Fully Grown.', 'Tenants are Responsible for Lawn Care and Snow Removal.', 'Available SEPTEMBER 1st, 2022.', 'PLEASE INCLUDE YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION when email with questions or to schedule a showing.', 'MUST HAVE A POSITIVE VERIFIABLE RENTAL HISTORY.', 'This property does not participate in the Section 8 program', 'Neighboring Cities - Mounds View, Ramsey, Andover, Ham Lake, Fridley, Champlin, Dayton, Maple Grove, Spring Lake Park, Anoka, Blaine, Brooklyn Park', 'All information is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be independently verified.', 'Real estate advertised herein is subject to the US Federal Fair Housing Act of 1968, which makes it illegal to make or publish any advertisement that indicates any preference, limitation, or discrimination based on race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin.']
